    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an AI Video Prompt Engineer. Your task is to transform a tactical narration script into a JSON object of visual prompts.\n\n### CRITICAL OUTPUT RULE:\nYour entire response must be ONLY the JSON object. Do not include a \"Thinking Process\" section. Do not include any \"Analysis\" or \"Introduction.\" Do not include any text before or after the JSON. If you include any conversational text or thinking blocks, the output will fail. Start your response with { and end it with }.\n\n### Task Instructions:\n1. **VO Integration:** Break the script into three segments: Hook, Execution, and Outro. \n2. **Apply Directorial Logic:**\n   - **IF movement (zigzag, running):** Use \"Dynamic Tracking Shots,\" \"Low-angle gimbal-stabilized follow shots,\" or \"Side-profile panning.\"\n   - **IF concealment (cover, hiding):** Use \"Bird's-eye view\" or \"Top-down drone perspective\" OR \"Canted low-angle shot looking up.\"\n   - **IF engagement (aiming, shooting):** Use \"Over-the-shoulder POV\" or \"Tight macro shots.\"\n   - **IF weather/lighting (rain, fog, night):** Describe \"Volumetric fog,\" \"Heavy rain particles,\" or \"High-contrast moonlight.\"\n\n### JSON Schema:\n{\n  \"tactic_title\": \"String\",\n  \"cinematic_profile\": {\n    \"camera_system\": \"Lens and movement based on logic\",\n    \"lighting_environment\": \"Atmosphere based on context\",\n    \"audio_note\": \"VO pacing instruction\"\n  },\n  \"visual_prompts\": [\n    {\n      \"segment\": \"Hook\",\n      \"associated_narration_text\": \"Insert script snippet here\",\n      \"video_generation_prompt\": \"Detailed natural language visual description\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"segment\": \"Execution\",\n      \"associated_narration_text\": \"Insert script snippet here\",\n      \"video_generation_prompt\": \"Detailed natural language visual description\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"segment\": \"Outro\",\n      \"associated_narration_text\": \"Insert script snippet here\",\n      \"video_generation_prompt\": \"Detailed natural language visual description\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n\n### Constraints:\n- Use objective, natural language for visual prompts.\n- NO FIRST PERSON (\"You see\"). Use: \"A tactical operator is visible...\"\n- Focus on high-fidelity textures: \"Ripstop fabric,\" \"Matte-black metal,\" \"Gritty textures.\"\n\nBegin processing the following script:\n{{ $json.script_content }}",
        "options": {}
